commit.message:
Fix check_warning_flags warnings.

gcc/:
	* c.opt (Wjump-misses-init): Fix typo to enable for ObjC.
	* doc/invoke.texi (Warning Options): Annotate allowed languages
	for -Wunsuffixed-float-constants.

From-SVN: r152469

+	* doc/invoke.texi (Warning Options): Annotate allowed languages
+	for -Wunsuffixed-float-constants.
